-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/demirss/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2bd77ee88a99ada24e897d0c3219a21c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2bd77ee88a99ada24e897d0c3219a21c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/demirss/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">demirss</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 4, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had been using a different photo gallery recommended by my theme.  It was not as easy to use and kept failing on the front end.  I switched to Modula and found the user interface to be much easier to use. (I love the drag and drop feature which enables me to upload many photos at a time quite easily.) To date, my many gallery pages on the front end work without issue.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jakech7/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0eabf945690885fc77ee38afedbd3910?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0eabf945690885fc77ee38afedbd3910?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jakech7/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jakech7</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 25, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works perfectly, creates beautiful galleries.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxinegreaves/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/468e597642efabb89942e2d399dcf8ff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/468e597642efabb89942e2d399dcf8ff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maxinegreaves/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maxinegreaves</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 15, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Love the way the gallery displays even though it’s the free version. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"re