----</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/bones-in-the-sand\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/bones-in-the-sand</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nA dead acacia tree against the sunlit sands of Deadvlei in Namibia during sunrise.<br />\n<br />\nDelving into the archives and finding not only work that I\'ve never published before, but also new photos to work on. Going to spend more time concentrating on my fine-art work and my photography workshops. Check out <a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com</a> for more info on both!<br />\n<br />\nAlso head to <a href=\"http://www.acanela.com/finland-northern-lights/\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.acanela.com/finland-northern-lights/</a> for my next aurora workshop!<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 100 / f/8 / 1/400s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 145mm / Location: Deadvlei, Namibia</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1228:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/bones-in-the-sand\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/bones-in-the-sand</a></b> \n\nA dead acacia tree against the sunlit sands of Deadvlei in Namibia during sunrise.\n\nDelving into the archives and finding not only work that I\'ve never published before, but also new photos to work on. Going to spend more time concentrating on my fine-art work and my photography workshops. Check out <a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com</a> for more info on both!\n\nAlso head to <a href=\"http://www.acanela.com/finland-northern-lights/\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.acanela.com/finland-northern-lights/</a> for my next aurora workshop!\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 100 / f/8 / 1/400s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 145mm / Location: Deadvlei, Namibia</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/8395/28435171090_bb9274d2f8_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/8395/28435171090_bb9274d2f8_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/8395/28435171090_bb9274d2f8.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1470140345\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2014-05-26T07:28:47-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:14:\"May 26th, 2014\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/28435171090\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/8395/28435171090_bb9274d2f8_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/8395/28435171090_bb9274d2f8_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"683\";s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1024\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"500\";s:4:\"tags\";s:565:\"tsauchab travelphotography bark namib republiekvannamibië orange deadend claypan african thefella namibnaukluft photo dunes acacia landscape d800 vlei sanddunes arid photograph postprocessing saltpan digital africa dry sand namibia deadvlei photoshop republicofnamibia morning dune dslr tree photography conormacneill acaciaerioloba southernafrica desert treetrunk republiknamibia nationalpark trunk namibian tsauchabriver processing slr trees marsh subsaharan sossusvlei vachelliaerioloba park travel thefellaphotography light nikon clay sunrise branches dead pan\";s:5:\"tagsa\";a:62:{i:0;s:8:\"tsauchab\";i:1;s:17:\"travelphotography\";i:2;s:4:\"bark\";i:3;s:5:\"namib\";i