 across the Saharan sand dunes in the Erg Chebbi in Southern Morocco. A couple of years ago, as part of a job photographing a hotel in Morocco, I had to shoot their luxury desert camps in Erg Chebbi, near the Algerian border. I had an amazing driver who would take me over the massive sand dunes in the middle of nowhere. On one of these trips, we got to the top of some of the highest dunes and I spotted a this camel in the distance. This was shot at 300mm, so it was pretty far away!<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/5.6 / 1/1600s / Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6 @ 300mm / Location: Erg Chebbi, Morocco</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1220:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.500px.com/thefella\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">500px</a> | <a href=\"https://steller.co/thefella\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Steller</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/lone-camel\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/lone-camel</a></b> \n\nA lone camel walks across the Saharan sand dunes in the Erg Chebbi in Southern Morocco. A couple of years ago, as part of a job photographing a hotel in Morocco, I had to shoot their luxury desert camps in Erg Chebbi, near the Algerian border. I had an amazing driver who would take me over the massive sand dunes in the middle of nowhere. On one of these trips, we got to the top of some of the highest dunes and I spotted a this camel in the distance. This was shot at 300mm, so it was pretty far away!\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/5.6 / 1/1600s / Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6 @ 300mm / Location: Erg Chebbi, Moroc