dth=\"240\" height=\"160\" alt=\"Roadblock\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.500px.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">500px</a> | <a href=\"https://steller.co/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Steller</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/roadblock\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/roadblock</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nA reindeer crosses a wintery road deep inside the Arctic Circle in Finnish Lapland. <br />\n<br />\nI had been travelling around the Arctic Circle in the very north of Finland for a week, shooting a car campaign for Ford. It was the last day and we had a long way to drive to get to the next airport in Ivalo. On the way, we saw some reindeer in the trees and stopped to shoot them, as there unsurprisingly isn\'t much traffic in the Arctic. I looked out the back window and saw this one trying to sneak across the road.<br />\n<br />\nIf you\'re interested, you can also check out <a href=\"https://thefella.com/commission/ford-kugadventure\" rel=\"nofollow\">my other Ford shots</a>.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 800 / f/5.6 / 1/250s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 300mm / Location: Arctic Circle, Finland</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1315:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.500px.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">500px</a> | <a href=\"https://steller.co/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Steller</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/roadblock\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/roadblock</a></b> \n\nA reindeer crosses a wintery road deep inside the Arctic Circle in Finnish Lapland. \n\nI had been travelling around the Arctic Circle in the very north of Finland for a week, shooting a car campaign for Ford. It was the last day and we had a long way to drive to get to the next airport in Ivalo. On the way, we saw some reindeer in the trees and stopped to shoot them, as there unsurprisingly isn\'t much traffic in the Arctic. I looked out the back window and saw this one trying to sneak across the road.\n\nIf you\'re interested, you can also check out <a href=\"https://thefella.com/commission/ford-kugadventure\" rel=\"nofollow\">my other Ford shots</a>.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 800 / f/5.6 / 1/250s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 300mm / Location: Arctic Circle, Finland</i>\n\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4786/40884343862_2d2141a03b_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4786/40884343862_2d2141a03b_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4786/40884343862_2d2141a03b.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1521578805\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2016-11-15T08:25:01-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:19:\"November 15th, 2016\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/40884343862\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4786/40884343862_2d2141a03b_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4786/40884343862_2d2141a03b_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"683\";s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1024\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"500\";s:4:\"tags\";s:426:\"finnish northerneurope travelphotography finla